headline.main: BALTIMORE HAILS WINDSORS WILDLY; Formal Welcome Is at City Hall -- Festive Throng Lines Streets to Cheer Them 200,000 LINE THE STREETS Duke Expresses His Gratitude for America's Moral and Material Aid to Britain

lead_paragraph: BALTIMORE, Oct. 13 -- The Duke and Duchess of Windsor waved and turned their smiles on more than 200,000 festive citizens here today who fought to watch the progress of the couple through the city streets from the City Hall, where the ducal pair received an official welcome from Baltimore.
abstract: Duke of Windsor states gratitude for moral and material aid to Brit
